# Bulwark-Docker

A collection of Dockerfiles related to the [Bulwark](https://www.bulwarkcrypto.com) project.

## bulwark-build

Creates Linux 64 Bulwark binaries from scratch.

## bulwark-node 

Creates a working bulwark Linux64 node by installing bulwarkd/bulwark-cli and setting up a user bulwark with the needed configuration. Any parameters you add to the `run command will be added as configuration lines to bulwark.conf

## kovri

Sets up Kovri and configures a Bulwark service.

## tor 

Sets up a TOR server and configures it for Bulwark.